---
to: "{{ output }}"
description: |
  Generates a category-specific DTR test class for all jotp primitives
  in that category. One test method per primitive; one section per method.
  SPARQL results: rows keyed by (name, javaClass, javaGenerics?, description,
                                 methodName?, methodSig?, methodDesc?)
  Used by rules: core-process-doc-test, supervision-doc-test,
                 state-doc-test, error-doc-test, runtime-doc-test
---
